```class Solution {
    public String baseNeg2(int n) {
        if (n == 0) return "0";
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        while (n != 0) {
            int remainder = n % (-2);
            if (remainder < 0) {
                n += 2;
                sb.append('-');
            } else {
                n /= -2;
                sb.append(remainder == 1 ? '1' : '0');
            }
        }
        return sb.reverse().toString();
    }
}```
